Menene bikin Global Citizenship Festival kuma shin sun yi wani abu don kawar da talauci?
A ranar Asabar mai zuwa, za a yi bikin kiɗa na shekara-shekara a birnin New York, wanda zai ba da gudummawa ga manyan taurari, kuma zai yi aiki mai mahimmanci don kawar da talauci a duniya.
A wannan shekara ta bakwai ta bikin Global Citizen, dubban miliyoyin mutane za su taru a babban gonar Central Park ba don jin daɗin zane-zane na masu fasaha kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba kawai, amma don yada ainihin manufar bikin, wanda shine kawo ƙarshen talauci mai zafi a duniya ta 2030.
An kaddamar da bikin Global Citizens Festival a shekara ta 2012, wanda shine fadada tsarin shirin Global Poverty Project, wani shiri na duniya wanda ke da fatan samun karin mutane da ke kokarin kawar da talauci.
Don samun damar shiga wannan bikin kyauta (idan ba ku son siyan VIP ba), masu sauraron bikin dole ne su yi ayyuka ko "aiki" na gaba ɗaya kamar su ba da kansu don yada manufar kawar da duniya, aika imel, kiran waya, ko kuma duk wani abu mai ma'ana.
Amma yaya Global Citizens ya yi nasara a cikin shekaru 12 da suka rage don cimma burin?
Shin ra'ayin yin wa'azi kyauta ga jama'a hanya ce mai kyau na sa mutane su yi aiki ko kuma wani nau'i na abin da ake kira "clicktivism" wanda mutane ke ganin ya yi wani tasiri ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takardar shaidar kan layi ko kuma aikawa da tweet?
Global Citizen ta ce tun daga shekarar 2011 sun samu rahotanni cewa masu goyon bayansu sun yi fiye da miliyan 19 na "aiki" don dalilai daban-daban.
Ya ce, ayyukan su na taimaka wa shugabannin duniya su yi alkawari da manufofi na kudade da suka kai dala biliyan 3700 ko fiye, wanda zai shafi mutane sama da biliyan 225 nan da shekarar 2030.
A farkon shekarar 2018, kungiyar ta ba da sanarwar alkawura da sanarwar da suka biyo bayan ayyukanta, 390 daga cikinsu, an riga an ba da ko an tattara kudade na akalla dala biliyan 1.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa, kudaden da aka samu sun shafi rayuwar kusan mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Wasu manyan alkawuran sun hada da Power of Nutrition, haɗin gwiwar masu saka jari da masu shirya abinci a Burtaniya, wanda "yana taimaka wa yara su ci gaba da cikawa" kuma ya yi alkawarin bayar da dala miliyan 35 ga kasar don kawar da rashin abinci mai gina jiki a Rwanda, bayan sun samu tweets sama da 4,700 daga al'umma a duniya.
Tare da taimakon gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin ƙasa da kuma 'yan ƙasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya yin rashin adalci na zamantakewar abinci mai gina jiki a matsayin tushen tarihi, "in ji mai gabatar da Maganin Gina Jiki Tracey Ulman, mai gabatar da jawabi ga masu sauraro a wani kide kide a watan Afrilu 2018.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce bayan da aka yi fiye da ayyuka 5,000 don inganta abinci mai gina jiki na iyaye mata da yara a cikin Burtaniya, gwamnati ta sanar da samar da kudade don aikin Power of Nutrition, wanda zai kai ga mata da yara miliyan 50 tare da taimakon abinci mai gina jiki.
A cikin tambayoyin da ake yawan yi a shafin su, suna amsa tambayar nan, "Me ya sa kake ganin za mu iya kawar da talauci mai tsanani?"
Wani mai suna Global Citizen ya ce: "Wannan zai zama hanya mai wuya da kuma ta wuya - wani lokacin za mu yi kasawa kuma mu kasa.
Amma kamar yadda muka yi a dā, za mu yi nasara a kan kare hakkin dan adam da kuma nuna bambanci, domin mu kasance tare kuma mu kara samun ƙarfi.
