Amurka za ta iya amfani da rundunar sojin ruwa ta Amurka don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha - Sakataren Tsakiya
Sakataren harkokin wajen Amurka Ryan Zink ya bayyana cewa Washington za ta yi amfani da rundunar soji "idan ya cancanta" don hana makamashin Rasha shiga wasu kasuwannin da suka hada da na Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Washington Examiner.
Zink ya yi zargin cewa, shigar da Rasha cikin Syria - musamman ma inda Rasha ke aiki a kan gayyatar da gwamnatin ta ba ta da izini - ya zama hujja don gano sabbin kasuwanni na makamashi.
Zink ya ce: "Saboda suna cikin Gabas ta Tsakiya, ina ganin suna son yin amfani da makamashi kamar yadda suke yi a gabashin Turai, a kudancin Turai".
Kuma jami'ai sun ce, wadannan hanyoyi ne da kuma kayan aiki.
"Amma, Amurka tana da ikon yin amfani da jiragen ruwa idan ya cancanta, don tabbatar da cewa jiragen ruwa na teku suna buɗewa don tabbatar da cewa ba za su isa kasuwa ba", in ji shi.
Yana magana ne a gaban masu halarta a wani taron da kungiyar Zinc Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya, wadda ke aiki ne bisa ka'idar riba, wadda ta ce kanta ita ce "muryar masu amfani da makamashi" a Amurka.
Ya kwatanta matsayin Washington a kan ayyukan da ake yi tsakanin Rasha da Iran, kuma ya nuna cewa suna da tasiri iri ɗaya.
"Amfani da man fetur da kuma maye gurbin man fetur ne mafi arha a gaban Iran da Rasha", in ji shi, ya kira Rasha "Won Trick Pony" kuma ya ce tattalin arzikin Rasha ya dogara da man fetur.
An yi wannan sanarwar ne a lokacin da gwamnatin Trump ke kokarin maye gurbin Rasha, wadda ta fi kudin da masu amfani da Turai za su iya yi ta hanyar fitar da iskar gas zuwa Turai.
A cewar Trump, jami'an gwamnatin Trump da shugaban Amurka Donald Trump suna kokarin sa Jamus ta fita daga aikin Nord Stream 2 da aka yi da "ba daidai ba", wanda Trump ya ce ya sa Moscow ta "rubuce" Berlin.
Moscow ta sake jaddada cewa, aikin famfo na Nord Stream 2 mai nauyin dala biliyan 1,100 wanda zai ninka karfin da ake da shi a yanzu zuwa 11,000 m3 mai karfin gaske, yana da matukar tasiri.
Kremlin ya yi jayayya cewa Washington ta yi hamayya da wannan aikin ne kawai saboda dalilai na tattalin arziki, kuma wannan misali ne na rashin adalci.
"Irin wutar lantarki ba zai iya zama hanyar matsa lamba ba, kuma ina ganin muna da ra'ayi ɗaya cewa ya kamata masu amfani su zaɓi masu samarwa", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Alexander Novak bayan ganawa da Sakataren Makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry a Moscow a watan Satumba.
Jamus ta yi matukar damuwa da manufar Amurka, kuma Jamus ta yi alkawarin yin hakan.
Hukumar samar da masana'antu ta Jamus, Federation of German Industries (BDI), ta nemi Amurka ta yi nesa da manufofin makamashi na EU da yarjejeniyar Berlin da Moscow.
"A gare ni, babban abin tambaya ne a lokacin da wata ƙasa ta uku ta shiga tsakani a cikin samar da wutar lantarki", in ji Daiter Kemp, shugaban kungiyar masana'antun Jamus (BDI), bayan ganawar da ta yi da shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
'Yan majalisar Massachusetts sun ce za su "yi hankali sosai" da zaben shugaban kasa na 2020.
A ranar Asabar, Elizabeth Warren, 'yar majalisa a Massachusetts ta ce za ta "yi hankali" da zaben shugaban kasa da ke tafe bayan zaben tsaka-tsakin.
A lokacin da yake zama a garin Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ya tabbatar da cewa zai yi tunanin yin takara.
"Yanzu lokaci ya yi da mata za su koma Washington su yi sarauta a kan gwamnatin da ta rushe, kuma hakan ya haɗa da yin aiki na mata a matsayin babban jami'in gwamnati", in ji The Hill.
"Bayan 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zan yi hankali sosai ga zaben shugaban kasa".
Warren ya yi muhawara da Trump a zauren gari, yana cewa Shugaba Donald Trump "yana kaiwa wannan gundumar cikin mummunan hanya".
Ya ce, "Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump yake yi wa dimokiradiyya".
Warren ya yi magana a fili game da Trump da kuma Kawanu, waɗanda suka nada su a kotun koli.
A wani sakon da ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter a ranar Juma'a, Warren ya ce, "Tabbas muna bukatar FBI ta bincika mu kafin mu kada kuri'a".
Amma, wani bincike da aka fitar a ranar Alhamis ya nuna cewa yawancin mazauna mazabar Warren ba su son su yi takarar shugaban kasa a shekarar 2020.
