Rahoton da Hukumar Kula da Kifi da Dabi'a ta Florida ta fitar ya nuna cewa yawan ruwan Red Tide a yankin Tampa Bay ya ragu.
FWC ta ce ana samun rahoton cutar Pachier Bloom a Pinellas, Manate, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier Counties - wanda hakan ya rage yawan kwayoyin.
Red Tide ta faɗaɗa gabar tekun ta mil 130 daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudancin Li Counties.
Ana iya samun wuraren da ake samun 'yanci a kusan mil 10 na gabar teku a gundumar Hillsborough, amma a ƙasa da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma samu ruwan Red Tide a cikin gundumar Pasco.
"A makon da ya gabata an lura da matsakaitan taro a cikin Pinellas County ko a bakin teku, ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a bakin tekun Hilleborough County, manyan taro a cikin Manate County, manyan taro a kan babbar hanya ko a bakin tekun a Sarasota County, matsakaitan taro a cikin Charlotte County, manyan taro a cikin Li County ko a bakin tekun, da ƙananan taro a cikin County Collier.
Ana samun rahoton rashin lafiyar kai a Pinellas, Manate, Sarsota, Lee da Coolar Counties.
A makon da ya gabata, ba a samu wani ciwon numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida ba.
